>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">45%</span></p></td> </tr> <tr>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">AXA/AIA/中人寿</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">储蓄分红险（真智珍宝/爱无忧/简爱延续/盈丰宝）</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">20</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">30%</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">35%</span></p></td> </tr> <tr>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">保诚</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">大额储蓄分红险（隽升）</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">10</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">25%</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">30%</span></p></td> </tr> <tr>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">ALL</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">怀孕亲子计划、其他附加消费险（住院医疗、意外险等）</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">10%</span></p></td>  <td><p align="center"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">10%</span></p></td> </tr></tbody></table><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;"><br /></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">2、发放币种：HKD（与保单币种保持一致）;</span></p><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">3、自有单范围是指：员工本人及其直系亲属（父母、配偶、子女、兄弟、姐妹）；</span></p><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">4、所有险种的提成标准皆以基本供款年限为准，实际提成比=实际提成比例以基本供款年限比例为上限。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">5、所有保单须于冷静期满后方可计算业绩及提成；</span></p><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">6、发放时间：每月30日前与绩效工资同时发放。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;"><br /></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">五、本方案自2015年7月1日起执行，直至另行通知。</span></p><p align="right"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;巨牛投资（中国）控股有限公司</span></p><p align="right"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2015年7月24日</span></p>');
