(4166, 'content', '<p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;&nbsp;<wbr>&nbsp;<a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=eba446850102vu7j&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/004jy6Z7ty6UYcaInGY84" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(90, 105, 63);"><img src="http://s5.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6UYcaInGY84&amp;690" real_src="http://s5.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6UYcaInGY84&amp;690" width="500" height="334" name="image_operate_98431440687473552" alt="A股跌出价值洼地&nbsp;<wbr>迎来建仓良机" title="A股跌出价值洼地&nbsp;<wbr>迎来建仓良机" action-data="http%3A%2F%2Fs5.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F004jy6Z7ty6UYcaInGY84%26690" action-type="show-slide" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;" /></a><br /><br /></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 30px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">8<span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">月</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">27</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">日，大盘走势终于让</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">A</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">股投资者们松了一口。今日两市大幅高开后强势上扬，沪指重回</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3000</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点。</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">13:47</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">过后，两市跳水翻绿，沪指一度逼近</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">2900</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点。</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">14:15</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">分之后，两市没有再度跳水，而选择暴力拉升，沪指重上</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3000</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点。截至收盘，沪指涨</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">5.34%</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">，报</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3083.59</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点，成交</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">4043</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">亿元；深成指涨</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3.58%</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">，报</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">10254.3</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点，成交</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3610</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">亿元。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 30px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">巨牛金融认为，这个反弹来得十分恰到好处，有提振士气的作用。外围市场上，让投资者们担心的美股走势昨天收出大阳，暴跌行情出现止跌企稳的迹象。技术面上，<span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">A</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">股恐慌性的暴跌已经有所收敛，且从</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">60</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">分钟走势图中我们可以明显看到短暂企稳的形态，这个调整属于</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">C</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">浪下跌的最后一波，这波调整也接近尾声了。消息面上，股期指货收到严格监管，</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">26</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">日晚上中金所发布通知，对</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">152</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">名单日开仓量超过</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">600</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">手等</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">164</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">名客户采取限制开仓</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">1</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">个月的监管措施。虽然这话说得十分隐晦，但是我们还是可以感觉到这种做空的力量短期已经受到控制了。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 30px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">板块方面，金融三剑客对指数大涨贡献有力。银行、保险、券商集体走强，中国平安、中信银行、长江证券等集体涨停。我们分析，这是因为大金融板块确实存在超跌现象，机构扫货首选安全边际高、有业绩支撑的大金融板块。投资者后期也可以关注券商行情是否卷土重来，证券公司最近出尽利空，后市相对乐观。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 30px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">近期，因为市场动荡，两融余额再次出现快速下降。在过去<span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">7</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">个交易日中，两市融资余额下降逾</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">2000</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">亿元。根据和讯数据，截至</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">8</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">月</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">26</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">日，沪深两市融资余额报</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">10370</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">亿元，回到今年年初的水平。</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">8</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">月</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">17</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">日至</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">26</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">日间，两市融资余额从回升过程中的阶段性高点</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">13090</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">亿元跌落至</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">10370</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">亿元，净流出</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">2720</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">亿元，</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">8</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">个交易日内降幅达</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">20%</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">。这对于融资客又是毁灭性的打击，巨牛金融提醒投资者，股票是一个高风险的市场，要学会敬畏，千万不要贪图利益误用杠杆工具，最终误了自己。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 30px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:16px;">操作策略上，我们谨慎乐观，首先看到第一压力位<span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3120</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">—</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3200</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">一带，如果冲不上去可以适当高抛，风险点位在前期低点</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">2850</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">，如果低于这个位置要果断止损，市场不排除存在继续探底的可能性。如果将时间轴拉长，这一定是一个价值洼地，很多优质个股已经非常值得投资，投资者可以采取分批建仓的策略，越跌越买，然后耐心等待大盘回暖。</span></span></span></p>'),
(4167, 'content', '<p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(226, 236, 225);"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=eba446850102vunt&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/004jy6Z7ty6V4z09sZk22" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(90, 105, 63);"><img name="image_operate_24941441032511333" src="http://s3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6V4z09sZk22&amp;690" real_src="http://s3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6V4z09sZk22&amp;690" alt="大盘维持震荡攀升&nbsp;<wbr>金九银十迎来调仓良机" title="大盘维持震荡攀升&nbsp;<wbr>金九银十迎来调仓良机" action-data="http%3A%2F%2Fs3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F004jy6Z7ty6V4z09sZk22%26690" action-type="show-slide" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none;" /></a><br /><br /></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(226, 236, 225);"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 21pt;">8<span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">月</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">31</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">日，</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 21pt;">两市早盘双双低开，随后在低位震荡，沪指盘中一度跌逾<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3%</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">。午后，大盘一度跌近</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">4%</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">，不过随后震荡回升，收盘时沪指跌幅不足</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">1%</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">。值得注意的是，尾盘市场走势出现分化，小盘股下挫而大盘股拉升。热点方面，银行、保险等金融股逆市上涨。</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 21pt;">沪指</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 21pt;">收盘</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 21pt;">跌</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 21pt;">0.82%<span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">，报</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3205.99</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 21pt;">，深成指收<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">2.32%</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">，报</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">10549.16</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 21pt;">。两市成交量继续萎缩，合计成交<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">7963</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">亿元。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(226, 236, 225);"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">上周五收盘后，市场频频传出重磅利好，先是加大股指期货的交易成本，再限制期货合约的开仓交易量。</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">对沪深<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">300</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">、中证</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">500</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">、上证</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">50</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">股指期货各合约单日开仓交易量超过</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">100</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">手的，认定是单日开仓交易量较大的异常交易行为，而此前认定标准是</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">600</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">手。</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">我们认为</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">这是市场维稳阶段的</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">政策利好</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">，</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">短期将遏制股指期货的投机性，</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">中期</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">将引导机构投资者将股指期货当作套保工作，长期利好</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">中国股市</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(226, 236, 225);"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">技术层面，巨牛金融认为，</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">大盘</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">今日处于调整关口，反弹至<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点的第一缺口位需要经过消化、洗盘之后才有望</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">向第二涨幅目标<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3340</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点前进</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">。</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">大盘即便有机会向第二目标前进过程也不会一帆风顺，过程依然会有震荡伴随。如果这里</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">得不到</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">有效突破，那么短线</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">就还有宽幅调整的风险</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">，</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">建议投资者控制</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">仓位</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">。<strong>如果大盘触碰到<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3082</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">五天均线，就要坚决减仓躲避回调。</span></strong></span><strong><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">形成</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">岛形反转的初步条件必须突破站稳<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3340</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点附近，</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">在</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">这位置前必然多空会有博弈。</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(226, 236, 225);"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">尾盘中小板集体跳水，金融三剑客则成为领头羊，带领大盘站上<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3200</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">点，令投资者大跌眼镜。中证</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">500</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">今天跌幅</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">3.82%</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">，而代表大盘蓝筹的上证</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">50</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">则上涨</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">2.34%</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">，这是近段时间来中小板与大盘蓝筹出现分道扬镳的重要信号。这说明市场大量机构主力资金在寻求价值回归的操作布局，所以更多的放到低估蓝筹和被错杀的国资改革概念上，同时超跌严重的个股表现也总体不错；而大量的前期炒作疯狂过后的小盘题材和补跌的高位题材股则杀跌惨烈，有的创业板小盘题材暴跌了依然跌跌不休，这其实就是估值泡沫透支的自然回归。<strong>因此，我们建议投资者关注证券板块以及“一路一带”大盘蓝筹股后市能否持续领涨，可能是慢牛启动前的一个重要型号。</strong></span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(226, 236, 225);"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">券商股自</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">2014<span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">年</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">4<span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">季度大涨之后</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">一直处于消化吸收估值的阶段。在</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">2014</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">年下半年</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">上证指数上涨</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">58%,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">券商板块上涨</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">190%;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">在</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">2015</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">年上半年</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">上证指数上涨</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">32%,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">券商板块下降</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">5%</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 5px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(50, 62, 50); font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: rgb(226, 236, 225);"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 24px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">考虑到&nbsp;<wbr><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">8</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">月</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">25</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">日晚间降息降准的利好因素</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">加之目前券商绝对股价已跌回本轮牛市启动之前水平。我们认为券商</span></wbr></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">估值水平合理，</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">具有长期投资价值</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">，</span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;">值得重点关注。金融改革也将推动券商业绩结构优化<span style="font-family:Times New Roman;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">,</span><span style="font-family:宋体;word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal;">重塑长期竞争力。</span></span><span style="word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>金九银十的行情下，券商股和“一路一带”的二线蓝筹能否卷土重来，这是我们应该密切关注的。</strong></span></span></p>'),
(4168, 'content', '<div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; padding-top: 5px;"><div style="overflow: hidden; text-align: center; padding: 0px 0px 34px; position: relative;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/004jy6Z7gy6V6OznP4D23" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"><img src="http://s4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7gy6V6OznP4D23" real_src="http://s4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7gy6V6OznP4D23" alt="" title="" action-data="http%3A%2F%2Fs4.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F004jy6Z7gy6V6OznP4D23" action-type="show-slide" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" /></a><a style="outline: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">&nbsp;</a></div></div><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;"><span style="word-spacing: normal;">9</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">月</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">1</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">日，沪深两市并没有迎来开门红，千股跌停的惨案再次发生。今日早盘双双跳空低开，沪指低开</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">1.50%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">。随后沪指震荡下行，盘中一度小幅跳水，击穿前期低点，不过此后就探底回升。午后，大盘维持震荡格局，不过市场走势严重分化，创业板指大跌逾</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">5%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">。热点方面，金融股护盘上涨，其余板块普跌。截至收盘，沪指跌</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">1.23%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">，报</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">3166.62</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">点；深证成指跌</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">3.67%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">，报</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">10162.52</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">点；创业板指跌</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">5.38%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">，报</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">1889.49</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">点。</span><br /></p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">这与巨牛金融昨天预测的情况相吻合，金融三剑客这些被低估的蓝筹股持续发力，力挽指数继续跳水。但是，今天的盘面不容乐观，二八分化非常严重，板块方面只有银行和证券这两大金融巨头起到指数维稳的作用，中小板和创业板出现了大量的跌停潮。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">消息面上，有两大利空导致大盘今天的千股跌停。第一，相关监管部门向辖区券商下发了关于进一步落实《关于清理整顿违法从事证券业务活动的意见》有关事项的通知，要求各证券公司应在前期核实工作的基础上，限期完成利用信息系统外部接入开展违法证券业务活动的清理整顿工作，并首次给出了时间表：<strong>场外配资存量规模在150亿以内的券商，必须在9月底前完成清理整顿工作。</strong>这给本身就孱弱的大盘带来了沉重一击，场外配资盘不计成本地出逃，不少中小票出现集中踩踏的现象。第二，<strong>今天国家统计局公布的制造业PMI为49.7%，比上月下降0.3个百分点，降至临界点以下，这表明制造业增长动力不足。</strong>这个消息的公布，造次证明中国经济增长放缓，资本加速流出A股市场。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">今天沪深500和上证50继续呈现分道扬镳的走势，上证500上涨0.9%，沪深500则下跌6.55%，两者差距继续扩大7.45%。蓝筹股可以提振指数但是无法提振人气，题材股全面杀跌带弱人气，市场似乎短期时间内表现得相当诡异，既让你看到多数个股的恐慌抛售，又让你看到指数的坚定维稳。这种大盘蓝筹的短期维稳带动不了中小板个股的集体跟风，单独的金融板块发力，然并卵，依旧挽回不了市场低迷的人气。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">目前技术派认为，大盘跌破3373点后，在技术面上就构成了破位，形成了C浪下跌。大盘的底部具体点位很难说，但是筑底的时间还为时尚早。C浪往往是延伸浪，最复杂也最折磨人。因此，在短期市场人气不足、新增资金不愿入市的情况下，我们建议投资者一定要轻仓操作，投资组合建议进行调整，尽量选择有国家队护盘的蓝筹权重股。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">明天是非常关键的一个交易日，如果深成指击穿前期低点9713点，创业板击穿1875点，那么这个市场会非常危险。<strong>一旦破位之后，深成指和创业板会走向漫漫寻底之路，而沪指则难逃拖累的命运。这段时间行情诡异，实在不适合散户进行操作，建议中小投资一定要轻仓操作，切勿满仓操底。</strong></p>'),
(4169, 'content', '<div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; padding-top: 5px;"><div style="overflow: hidden; text-align: center; padding: 0px 0px 34px; position: relative;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/004jy6Z7ty6VfMifKq2ee" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"><img src="http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6VfMifKq2ee" real_src="http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6VfMifKq2ee" alt="" title="" action-data="http%3A%2F%2Fs15.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F004jy6Z7ty6VfMifKq2ee" action-type="show-slide" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" /></a></div></div><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">9月7日，大盘冲高后回落，沪指临近收盘时蓝筹权重股带头向下跳水。截至收盘，沪指报3080.42点，跌幅2.52%；创业板指报1893.52点，涨幅2.07%。上证指数在出现了补跌行情，前期护盘积极的银行、保险、航空等蓝筹板块跌幅居前；而创业板则领涨，软件、安防、网贷、电子支付等概念板块涨幅居前。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">今天大盘的资金流向难言乐观，我们从大盘动向观测到，主力资金出逃，中小资金则一个劲儿地往里冲。这也就说明了，对于放假期间中央释放出来的利好，中小投资者欣然接受。巨牛金融的观点是，在大资金没有进场前，这个市场的投资风险大于机会。作为散户投资者，应该耐心等候市场底部走出来。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">资金方面，两融余额已经有了质的变化，截至9月2日，两融余额跌破万亿大关，降至9622亿。我们都知道，上轮牛市的启动，融资客成为这波行情的重要推手。经历了8月底的集体爆仓后，两融余额已经回到年初起点，而这波牛市的起点两融余额是在7000亿左右。可以说，目前大盘的点位距离中期底部的距离已经越来越近了。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;"><br /></p><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; padding-top: 5px;"><div style="overflow: hidden; text-align: center; padding: 0px 0px 34px; position: relative;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/004jy6Z7ty6VfM3NHz816" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"><img src="http://s7.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6VfM3NHz816" real_src="http://s7.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6VfM3NHz816" alt="" title="" action-data="http%3A%2F%2Fs7.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F004jy6Z7ty6VfM3NHz816" action-type="show-slide" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" /></a></div></div><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">股指期货的表现“抢眼”，但是冲进去的散户又会发现，为什么股指期货涨势汹汹，大盘依旧守不住继续往下探呢？这就是市场，市场总会给你制造出新的问题让你去应对。限得了股指期货，又救不了大盘，现在股指期货开始强于大盘上涨，而大盘却并没有随同期货上涨。其实，9月2日中金所宣布非套保交易单个产品日内开仓超过10手的，构成“日内开仓交易量较大”的异常交易行为，因此当前股指期货对现货市场的影响并没有原来那么大。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">短期操作上，投资者依然不能回避由清理融资带来的砸盘风险。据了解，某信托就接到了齐鲁证券关于清理违规配资账户的通知，旗下8只配资产品在清理名单之中。这也存在隐忧，如果是因为清理违规从事证券业务的相关账户，那么大盘可能会继续下探寻底。操作策略上，股权质押已经出现强平的上市公司，后市不容乐观，投资者应该警惕股权质押大面积爆仓引发的急跌。巨牛金融建议投资者控制仓位，切勿盲目追高，保持谨慎乐观的心态。</p>'),
(4170, 'content', '<div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; padding-top: 5px;"><div unselectable="on" style="position: relative; text-align: center; padding: 0px 0px 34px; overflow: hidden;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/004jy6Z7ty6VhUJOYAkbc" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"><img src="http://s13.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6VhUJOYAkbc" real_src="http://s13.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6VhUJOYAkbc" alt="" title="" action-data="http%3A%2F%2Fs13.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F004jy6Z7ty6VhUJOYAkbc" action-type="show-slide" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" /></a></div></div><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">9月8日<span style="word-spacing: normal;">，大盘低开后冲高震荡。午后，在银行股带动下，市场热点全面爆发，大盘触底反弹，临近收盘一度大涨逾</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">3%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">，但成交量大幅萎缩。截至收盘，沪指</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">3170.45</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">点，涨幅</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">2.92%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">；创业板指报</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">2001.16</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">点，涨幅</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">5.68%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">经过8月末的大幅调整，进入9月以来，监管层出台多项措施稳定股市，上证指数在3100点附近震荡筑底，不过两市成交额屡创新低，8日再刷新地量纪录，沪深股市分别成交2639亿和2603亿，合计仅为5242亿元，环比分别缩减了12.8%和13%，再创5个多月地量纪录。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">一个较为乐观的现象是，8日大盘的现货市场与股指期货相对持平，呈现出同步的走势，尾盘上涨伴随着放量。巨牛金融判断，中期大盘可能会有几天反弹机会，建议投资者抓住国企改革的龙头股。根据东方财富网提供的资金数据，我们观测到今天午后大盘的主力资金流入200多亿，这也就说明了市场其实并不缺钱，缺的是进场的机会与中长线持有的信心。回顾上一波牛市，券商股集体暴动与中国中车等指标股能否起到带头作用，也可以成为投资者进行参考的重要指标。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">9月8日大盘能够顺利站稳3000点，尤其是午后V型逆转千股涨停，简直就是给沉寂多天的市场打了鸡血。虽然说大盘打了个翻身仗，但是我们也不建议投资者过分乐观。因为从技术上分析，目前大盘依旧在2850点——3400点进行箱体震荡，只有3400点的箱体顶部强势突破，才能进入第二箱体位3400点——3800点进行调整，因此我们还是建议投资者走一步看一步，谨慎看多。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">正如我们昨天的复盘报告提及的一样，我们不要顺应这波反弹，但不要过分乐观，因为投资者依然不能回避由清理融资带来的砸盘风险。操作策略上，股权质押已经出现强平的上市公司，后市不容乐观，投资者应该警惕股权质押大面积爆仓引发的急跌。巨牛金融建议投资者控制仓位，切勿盲目追高，时刻防范市场风险。</p>'),
(4171, 'content', '<div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; padding-top: 5px;"><div style="overflow: hidden; text-align: center; padding: 0px 0px 34px; position: relative;"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/004jy6Z7ty6VjtwJXHoa6" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"><img src="http://s7.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6VjtwJXHoa6" real_src="http://s7.sinaimg.cn/mw690/004jy6Z7ty6VjtwJXHoa6" alt="" title="" action-data="http%3A%2F%2Fs7.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F004jy6Z7ty6VjtwJXHoa6" action-type="show-slide" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;" /></a></div></div><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;"><span style="word-spacing: normal;">9</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">月</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">9</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">日，</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">大盘震荡走高，沪指强势站稳</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">3200</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">点。截至收盘，沪指报</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">3243.09</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">点，涨幅</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">2.29%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">；创业板指报</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">2071.72</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">点，涨幅</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">3.53%</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">。从盘面看，软件、充电桩、锂电池等概念板块涨幅居前，市场热点表现活跃。银行、保险等权重板块涨幅滞后。</span><br /></p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">大盘此次上涨伴随着放量，沪深两市成交额达8400亿左右，我们暂时把这次定义为超跌反弹。短线交易上，应该密切深证成指10850，创业板2300这几个关键位置。<span style="word-spacing: normal;"><strong><span style="word-spacing: normal;">投资者还是要敬畏市场，警惕风险，不要保持七秒钟的记忆力，</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">因此需要控制仓位</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">、</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">预防风险。</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">这次反弹行情起点是货币政策、财政政策和非常规手段共振的结果。降准降息等货币政策和非常规前期已经使用多次，对市场起到的影响愈来愈小。目前看来，财政政策出来唱戏，效果立竿见影。<strong>在投资信心严重缺失的资本市场，光靠砸钱或者修改交易规则并不能重唤投资者买票的信心，实体经济的回暖才是决定信心是否回归的关键。</strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">近日，中国政府再次公布了提振人心的政策——增支减税。增支方面预测1.2万亿的专项建设债券首批3000亿已经确定，减税方面给出了积极的全面的方案。<span style="word-spacing: normal;"><strong>近期中国政府推出的政策组合拳频率之快、力度之大，有望在<span style="word-spacing: normal;">第三季度</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">、</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">第四季度的实体数据上</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">体现出来</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">，</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">从而</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">扭转近期市场的悲观情绪，因此</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">巨牛金融</span><span style="word-spacing: normal;">给予本轮反弹更大的信心。</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 22px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei'', Simsun; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px;">操作策略上，由于存在阅兵前指数维稳的政治护盘因素，巨牛金融认为目前沪指处于相对失真的状态，投资者此时应该拿深成指作为参考对象。一旦前期最低位10850点无法强势突破，那么极有可能反弹到此夭折，大盘继续下探。如果这一位置能顺利站稳，那么接下来可能会有一波较大级别的反弹。上海国资改革、迪斯尼概念的双重效应让上海板块成为龙头，重点关注超跌个股、低于定增价的可以重点关注。</p>');
